001package com.minimajack.v8.metadata.external.qualifier;
002
003import com.minimajack.v8.metadata.external.qualifier.impl.*;
004import com.minimajack.v8.transformers.AbstractTransformer;
005import com.minimajack.v8.transformers.impl.ObjectTransformer;
006import com.minimajack.v8.utility.SerializedOutputStream;
007import com.minimajack.v8.utility.V8Reader;
008
009import java.nio.ByteBuffer;
010
011public class QualityTransformer implements AbstractTransformer<Qualifiers> {
012
013  @Override
014  public Qualifiers read(final ByteBuffer buffer) {
015    buffer.mark();
016    Qualifiers readedQuality;
017    ObjectTransformer.readBracket(buffer);
018    final String enums = V8Reader.read(String.class, buffer);
019    buffer.reset();
020    switch (enums) {
021      case "N": {
022        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(NumberQualifiers.class, buffer);
023        break;
024      }
025      case "S": {
026        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(StringQualifiers.class, buffer);
027        break;
028      }
029      case "#": {
030        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(DbLinkQuality.class, buffer);
031        break;
032      }
033      case "D": {
034        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(DateQualifiers.class, buffer);
035        break;
036      }
037      case "B": {
038        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(BooleanQuality.class, buffer);
039        break;
040      }
041      case "U": {
042        readedQuality = V8Reader.read(UndefinedQuality.class, buffer);
043        break;
044      }
045      case "T": {
046        throw new RuntimeException("Unsupported type: " + enums);
047      }
048      default:
049        throw new IllegalStateException("Unexpected value: " + enums);
050    }
051    return readedQuality;
052  }
053
054  @Override
055  public void write(Object object, SerializedOutputStream buffer) {
056    throw new UnsupportedOperationException("Not implemented");
057  }
058
059}
